# Employee Tracker

![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green.svg)

Use this application to track employees, roles, and departments!

## Table of Contents
- [Description](#description)
- [License](#license)
- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [Questions](#questions)

## Description
This project leverages **Node.js** and **PostgreSQL** to store and manipulate information about employees. It keeps track of details such as salaries, positions, department roles, and hierarchical structures (e.g., who reports to whom). The application is designed to make employee data management efficient and straightforward.

